OL,3,CMan jailed for smashing glass in
OL,4,Cwoman's face after argument about
OL,5,Cgirlfriend
OL,7,FA man has been jailed for smashing
OL,8,Fglass into a woman's face at a pub
OL,9,Fafter she told him his girlfriend
OL,10,Fshould be able to decide whether to
OL,11,Fstay out with friends.
OL,13,FJordan Newbold, of St James Court in
OL,14,FHardwick, Stockton, wanted his
OL,15,Fgirlfriend to go home with him on the
OL,16,Fevening of May 13 2022 when the
OL,17,Fargument broke out at the Fairfield
OL,18,Fpub, a court was told.
