OL,7,FPub staff ordered Newbold, who worked
OL,8,Fas a pipe fitter, to leave the pub but
OL,9,Fhe insisted on waiting outside to
OL,10,Fspeak with the victim.
OL,12,FAn employee let the victim leave via a
OL,13,Fback entrance and drove her home.
OL,15,FTalking about the impact of the
OL,16,Fincident, the victim, who was left
OL,17,Fwith a scar on her lip, told Teesside
OL,18,FCrown Court she no longer wanted to go
OL,19,Fout with friends and family.
