OL,7,FNewbold initially pleaded not guilty
OL,8,Fto actual bodily harm, although he
OL,9,Flater admitted guilt.
OL,11,FHe also pleaded guilty to failing to
OL,12,Fsurrender to court after he missed one
OL,13,Fof his hearings, on Wednesday 24 April.
OL,15,FNewbold was later arrested for missing
OL,16,Fthe court date and was remanded in
OL,17,Fprison.
