OL,7,FDefending him, Michele Turner said
OL,8,FNewbold initially pleaded not guilty
OL,9,Fbecause he thought his actions were
OL,10,F"reckless" but has since realised the
OL,11,Fimpact of his actions.
OL,13,FMs Turner added he did not go to court
OL,14,Fas he was working.
OL,16,FWhile the judge told Newbold his
OL,17,Factions happened in a "momentary loss
OL,18,Fof control," the attack would have a
OL,19,Flifelong impact on the victim.
